Properties.femaleVariant: [en_us][GT]Come on, help me.
[en_us][GT]We'll take it off the top. And carefully. If it collapses, they're done.
[en_us][GT]Fuck me, I hope we'll be there first.
[en_us][GT]We grab everything as it comes, then we make a selection.
[en_us][GT]Fuck, come on. Man. We're here under arms, and what you see in front of you is a fucking barricade.
[en_us][GT]Normally I would consider that to be quite a clear message. Well, but you were fucking in the City last year.
[en_us][GT]So I will explain to you. THERE'S NO FUCKING PASSAGE.
[en_us][GT]To all residents of the Zone. This is Krausser.
[en_us][GT]Quit shaking like that. Grit your teeth. You'll be fine.
[en_us][GT]Okay, fuckin' chill. We're movin'.
[en_us][GT][jump into the chute] I have bad associations.
[en_us][GT]Eh. Dumpster. I have bad associations.
[en_us][GT]Go down the chute. It will be the fastest.
[en_us][GT]Shit ... I've never had such a pain in my life ...
[en_us][GT]But there are still so many things out there! Wait!
[en_us][GT]Focus now. You will not pass this way without a fight.
[en_us][GT]You are deliberately doing everything the opposite of what I am asking you to do, or are you trying, and just fucking up?
[en_us][GT]I already have one complainant in my head. I don't need any more.
[en_us][GT]I know your options, but we can't take any chances.
[en_us][GT]Okay, I'll go around them.
[en_us][GT]I'll do it my way.
[en_us][GT]Okay as you like. I'll be like a fly's shadow. They won't see me.
[en_us][GT]I will be grateful.
[en_us][GT]You chose me for this assignment. I trusted you. Now you have to trust me.
[en_us][GT]I will do what I see fit.
[en_us][GT]The three of us can't do it anyway.
[en_us][GT]Let's get the people together. We will make a line, we will dig them out in a few minutes.
[en_us][GT]You would need to organize some equipment, although basic, so as not to do everything with your bare hands.
[en_us][GT]Do you really think people will help us?
[en_us][GT]What line? For what? They are dead.
[en_us][GT]After all, they are their neighbors. Of course they will.
[en_us][GT]They're already done. What you are doing makes no sense.
[en_us][GT]Then you've had it real comfortable. Just some scratches.
[en_us][GT]I wonder what the fuck that was.
[en_us][GT]Apparently a plane.
[en_us][GT]Awaaaa! Be careful!
[en_us][GT]Quit screaming, or you'll be dressing your own wounds.
[en_us][GT]Krausser shot something down again?
[en_us][GT]Or they attacked us.
[en_us][GT]Will there be a new war?
[en_us][GT]S'posed to grit your teeth.
[en_us][GT]We pull the bodies aside, hide them so that no one can find them.
[en_us][GT]We do not cut immediately on the spot?
[en_us][GT]Nooo, you fucked up? Too little time. First you need to secure the goods.
[en_us][GT]Then we wait until no one is watching and only then do we cut.
[en_us][GT]Okay. Are we taking something from the wreckage?
[en_us][GT]What is possible. Electronics first and we don't check if it works or not.
[en_us][GT]Sure thing. Wires? Metal sheets? Personal things?
[en_us][GT]Yes. Yes. And yes.
[en_us][GT]Walk around them so that they can't see you. I insist.
[en_us][GT]I strongly advise against fighting.
[en_us][GT]I heard you the first time.
[en_us][GT]But I live there!
[en_us][GT]Don't give a fuck. Come on fucking leave.
[en_us][GT]It takes way too long.
[en_us][GT]I have something better. The first bike you find is yours.
[en_us][GT]You're not going any further.
[en_us][GT]Close your mouths and listen.
[en_us][GT]As you may have noticed, something dropped out of the fucking sky right on us.
[en_us][GT]And as you can imagine, the crash site is now a restricted zone.
[en_us][GT]What does it mean? It means don't fucking go there.
[en_us][GT]Unless you work for me and I told you to.
[en_us][GT]Everyone else - keep your asses away from the scene of the accident.
[en_us][GT]Until further notice.
[en_us][GT]I blocked the engine. Get off.
[en_us][GT]Then give me wings.
[en_us][GT]Shit, let's get the fuck outta here before they snatch what we've got!
[en_us][GT]B-b-but I saw braindance equipment there, I'll be back...
[en_us][GT]Fuck, someone's coming! Run!
[en_us][GT]Oh shit ... oh shit, oh shit ...
[en_us][GT]You get hit?
[en_us][GT]You didn't get on the bike.
[en_us][GT]Then run. Now every minute counts, V.
[en_us][GT]Oh, fuckin' preem. You can't get this anywhere.
[en_us][GT]Hurry up, okay?
[en_us][GT]Who is this clown from the loudspeaker?
[en_us][GT]Can you block these trucks?
[en_us][GT]That clown on the spekers, who is he?
[en_us][GT]These trucks ...
[en_us][GT]Come on, for fuck's sake.
[en_us][GT]Local warlord. Do not worry about him.
[en_us][GT]They are taking reinforcements to the scene of the accident.
[en_us][GT]And these trucks will not go anywhere anymore.
[en_us][GT]Thanks.
[en_us][GT]What's happening?
[en_us][GT]It would be good if they didn't arrive. Can it be arranged?
[en_us][GT]You do well. Give me a moment.
[en_us][GT]Hey, what are you doing !? You need to get to the wreckage as soon as possible!
[en_us][GT]V! The President needs help!
[en_us][GT]Holy shit, goddamn it!
[en_us][GT]What are you talking about?
[en_us][GT]What are you talking about? I haven't killed any president.
[en_us][GT]Don't overdo it, Songbird. I was trying to help.
[en_us][GT]Don't overdo it.
[en_us][GT]Pray that we don't meet again.
[en_us][GT]I trusted you. And I have given you one simple task: reach the wreckage.
[en_us][GT]Trying is not enough, V.
[en_us][GT]Nothing! I start it up and nothing!
[en_us][GT]Why we work with such shitty equipment?
[en_us][GT]Well, we have to go where that plane crashed. Krausser orders.
[en_us][GT]Then have Krausser come here and order the corpse to move on.
[en_us][GT]What do you have there?
[en_us][GT]Nothin'. Fuck off.
[en_us][GT]The fuck you mean? We were here first.
[en_us][GT]It doesn't mean that it belongs to you.
[en_us][GT]Nothing belongs to anyone. But we were here first, end of fuckin' discussion.
[en_us][GT]Find your own pile of junk.
[en_us][GT]Get lost or I'll fuck you up.
[en_us][GT]What is it?
[en_us][GT]Congratulations, V. You just contributed to the death of Rosalind Myers, President of NUSA.
[en_us][GT]You blew it. It's the same as if you pull the trigger.
[en_us][GT]Are you sure she's dead?
[en_us][GT]I'm sure.
[en_us][GT]No ... I don't think so ... But it was close ...
[en_us][GT]Thought I was a goner.
[en_us][GT]Better get gone. Might not be over yet.
[en_us][GT]Maybe this is just the beginning.
[en_us][GT]Oh shit ... You know something?
[en_us][GT]All I know is, if it blew up once, it can do it again.
[en_us][GT]Okay ... I'll ... I'll get moving.
[en_us][GT]My hands are going nuts. I have to calm down.
[en_us][GT]On the third day, at three o'clock, fire rained down from heaven and flooded the earth to the horizon!
[en_us][GT]Well no, I didn't have time to record it. It all happened too fast.
[en_us][GT]You're not going any further, end of fuckin' story.
[en_us][GT]V, keep going.
[en_us][GT]Time is running out. Move, move.
[en_us][GT]Why are you standing there? You should run.
[en_us][GT]Don't get distracted, hurry to the wreckage.
[en_us][GT]V! They are dying there.
[en_us][GT]Fuck, if you're not helping, at least don't run your fuckin' mouth We won't know if they're alive or dead until we take it off.
[en_us][GT]Okay, I'm not stupid. You said that already.
[en_us][GT]What are you bothering me with?
[en_us][GT]I want to know what happened. I have friends there.
[en_us][GT]What can I say? The plane crashed.
[en_us][GT]But what plane? Why? Krausser didn't tell you anything?
[en_us][GT]Nunya biz. Get lost.
[en_us][GT]Come on, dude. It was seconds.
[en_us][GT]I filmed what's going on here, people under the rubble, wounded, dead bodies.
[en_us][GT]It will definitely sell.
[en_us][GT]Don't piss me off. You think I don't know the crash would be better ?!
[en_us][GT]I know! But I didn't make it, okay ?!
[en_us][GT]I can't film the wreckage. They won't let anyone in there.
[en_us][GT]Fuck, we'll finally make some eddies. The fucking wreck's a gift from heaven.
[en_us][GT]Hey. I can see something. Give me some, be human.
[en_us][GT]We broke the bank, choom.
[en_us][GT]For your sins, for all wickedness, for hearing false prophets ...
[en_us][GT]God has sent you the bowels of hell!
[en_us][GT]I gave you signs, but you did not listen!
[en_us][GT]I have begged, but you have turned your ears away from my voice!
[en_us][GT]Now you will regret it, but it is too late!
[en_us][GT]You did not listen to the voice that cried out in the crowd, and the Lord punished you terribly for it!
[en_us][GT]Get ready to die! Death!!! Death turns red!
[en_us][GT]Forgive me, father, for I have sinned ...
[en_us][GT]You fool! Too late! Too late!
